question: What is the name of the administrative center of Cēsu novads (Cēsis county) in Latvia?
asked_question_translated: Vad heter det administrativa centrumet för Cēsu novads (Cēsis län) i Lettland?
answer: Det administrativa centrumet för Cēsu novads i Lettland heter Cēsis.
answer_translated_eng: The administrative centre of Cēsu novads in Latvia is Cēsis.
